snippet.title: Newsy Entertainment
snippet.description:
Keep current on the latest quality news in entertainment. We're not your celebrity gossip tabloid. You're sure to get quality journalism and content that really matters to your day... 

Get the news you need in short, unbiased videos and be the most informed person in the room. Bypass the bloviating talking heads and get straight to the facts so you can make your own opinions about the news that's changing your world.

Newsy accelerates your understanding of a news story and offers critical context from multiple sources. Break free from the bias, skip the sensationalism and escape the clickbait to get a fresh take on today’s top news. Newsy gives you “news with the why” through concise videos and full transcripts for every story. Find out for yourself why Newsy was called "the future of mobile news" by The Huffington Post. Subscribe Today.
